87}, {\"ngram\": \"McClenaghan\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think the human brain is meant to comprehend something like that fully.\\\"\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the human brain\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even the very best can fall' He remains philosophical about the fall in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9194110261282268, \"rank\": 0.087617392873097, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fall\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Su Weide fell twice from the high bars during the team competition in Paris.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999885705925098, \"rank\": 5.2902479988346625e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999683473112, \"rank\": 3.165262219972203e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the high bars\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the team competition\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the nature of gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the very best can fall, and fall multiple times,\\\" McClenaghan added.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McClenaghan\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all know it's a possibility.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just about who can hold their nerve in that moment and not make those big errors.\\\"\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their nerve\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"those big errors\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will return to Newtownards, a town in County Down, Northern Ireland, with his gold and every intention of using his own success to inspire future generations.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.97514707376478e-22, \"text\": \"Newtownards\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"score\": 0.9999998497739966, \"rank\": 1.5022607702427893e-07, \"text\": \"County Down\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996557563, \"rank\": 2.829346320604093e-10, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedi