to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mutual respect Gymnastics is an event that captures even the casual viewer's imagination at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9001584217394799, \"rank\": 0.10887343009634322, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mutual respect\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"even the casual viewer's imagination\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody from across the world in gymnastics, including the Chinese, we all have this mutual respect for each other,\\\" McClenaghan said highlighting the unity gymnasts share.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9432335751333577, \"rank\": 0.05995689181236246, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"this mutual respect\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"McClenaghan\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"the unity gymnasts\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all know how difficult it is just to get to the Olympic Games so when we see each other, it's a pleasure and we congratulate each other.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\